text:
*Welcome to the official Slack community for CBTC credential holders! We're excited to have you here.*

We've created this space to build a strong community, share important updates, and get your valuable feedback. This is a place for you to connect, ask questions, and stay informed.

As we move forward, your participation will be crucial in shaping the future of the ecosystem. We're particularly excited to brainstorm the next app we build on Canton and hear your thoughts on planned use cases for CBTC. Your insights as active users are invaluable.

We'll be using this channel to:
• Share updates on rewards and distribution schedules.
• Discuss potential new features and utilities.
• Gather your ideas for the future of CBTC and Canton.
Additionally, we believe your success is our success. We plan to reach out individually in the coming weeks to coordinate co-marketing efforts and explore how we can highlight the amazing things you're building.

We're looking forward to collaborating with you. Please feel free to introduce yourselves and start a conversation!

Best,

The BitSafe Team
